data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom home sitting on HUGE almost half an acre lot with 2 car garage, *RV PARKING, SWIMMING POOL, LOW HOA and stunning mountain views. Walk inside to the front living room and built in office space. Family room has ceiling fan light and is open to the dining area and updated kitchen that boasts stainless steel appliances, maple cabinets and walk in pantry. French doors from family room take you to the LARGE backyard that features swimming pool, large shed, patio, gazebo and side yard for RV parking. Lavish primary bedroom has ceiling fan light, walk in closet and primary upgraded bathroom with double sinks and huge his and his walk in shower!! *Zoned for horses* DON'T MISS OUT...VIEW TODAY!
